		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-2">    
				<h5><strong>What does being affiliated mean?<br></strong></h5>
				<p>Each nation will have it's own respective governing body, commonly known as a National Touch Association (NTA). By becoming an affiliated club you will then fall under the NTA governance. To find your NTA take a look <a href="http://toucheurope.org/site/membership/membership" target="_blank">here</a></p>    
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-4">
			  <h5><strong>Are there any fees involved?<br></strong></h5>    
			    <p>Each NTA will usually have their own membership fee structure and benefits for this membership will vary.</p>      
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
		  <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-2">
		    <h5><strong>What are the benefits of becoming affiliated?<br></strong></h5>    
				<p>Each NTA will offer their own benefits for being an affiliated club and usually charge a membership fee, benefits will vary so it is best to contact your NTA for further information.</p>
			</div> 
		  </div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

